Background task smoke test still fails after SQLite busy_timeout change: queued tasks remain queued with no pid/log/worktree even though daemon loop should poll them. Investigate whether the running daemon needs restart for the fix, whether background polling is actually active, and what start_queued_with_callback is doing in the live process.
